2097143826.text: "Here, we found overexpression of Best-3 inhibited TNFalpha induced IKKbeta and IkappaBalpha phosphorylation, blocked TNFalpha induced ubiquitination and subsequent degradation of IkappaBalpha, and suppressed the nuclear translocation of p65 and p50."
